  <dsc><c01 id="aspace_b6fd8a91d7539fdfa7d7d5aa6390fe78" level="item"><did><unittitle>Cornell University paddle</unittitle><unitid>MU-4118</unitid><unitdate certainty="approximate" datechar="creation" normal="1931/1934" type="inclusive">1931-1934</unitdate><physdesc id="aspace_f320fc47b93cf66f2c193c8c275e6d1f">Wooden paddle with Cornell University written on one side, and signatures on the other. Signed by Edward A Reed, Peter Carnesale, and other illegible signatures.</physdesc><container id="aspace_1adbffa18979a0e3aa10f0e568cd1577" label="Mixed Materials [31924113902906]" type="mu">4118</container></did></c01><c01 id="aspace_588e200559d2573d39110646ed52a372" level="item"><did><unittitle>Rothschild Bros. paper Cornell pennant</unittitle><unitid>MU-747</unitid><unitdate calendar="gregorian" datechar="creation" era="ce">Undated</unitdate><container altrender="Flat box, (24.5w x 20.5d x 3h)" id="aspace_197fced3501b929d447baa0127bb1a88" label="Realia [31924131171799]" type="box">1</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_57b17dd910b0f29e8e85f0b166c0cd8e"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>Red paper pennant with white "Cornell" on the front and "Pennants, Banners, Pillow Tops, Pictures: Rothschild Bros" on back.</p></scopecontent></c01><c01 id="aspace_d4ea7d5c8308bbb3ffb2e3fec2fa35a9" level="item"><did><unittitle>Triangle laundry tag</unittitle><unitid>MU-1033</unitid><unitdate calendar="gregorian" datechar="creation" era="ce">Undated</unitdate><container altrender="Flat box, (24.5w x 20.5d x 3h)" id="aspace_c53627e899d6fa3d3fd44bfb9d30ad3b" label="Realia [31924131171799]" type="box">1</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_99b71ac2130c5f9db463a54344745af8"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>Canvas triangle with accompanying note: "Believed to be tag for laundry case, which was sent home to be done."</p></scopecontent></c01><c01 id="aspace_a527d1456aa0d0dc5c503a75aa798487" level="item"><did><unittitle>Goldfish swallowing contest net</unittitle><unitid>MU-432</unitid><